claim: Vaccination with a higher-dose recombinant flu vaccine may induce a more robust antibody response than egg-based standard-dose vaccines.
explanation: Black-and-white image showing the U.S. Department of Health & Human Services seal on the left and the CDC logo on the right. does not support the claim because the image contains only organizational logos and no data or study findings regarding antibody responses to different flu vaccines.
